JDBCProxy Framework 2.3-SNAPSHOT API

Packages
net.big_oh.common.jdbc Provides classes that handle the "heavy lifting" involved in constructing a proxy for a JDBC Driver.
net.big_oh.common.jdbc.event Provides classes that encapsulate various JDBC operations as Java event objects.
net.big_oh.common.jdbc.event.listener Defines the interface for classes that listen for JDBC events.
net.big_oh.common.jdbc.event.listener.logger Implements listener classes that demonstrate logging JDBC events.
net.big_oh.common.jdbc.event.listener.safety Implements listener classes that demonstrate use of JDBC proxy to prevent the execution of dangerous SQL statements.
